have been just wonderful.

294
00:24:01,566 --> 00:24:03,567
Tomorrow, why don't we drive
up the coast

295
00:24:03,651 --> 00:24:05,569
to that little seafood place, and...

296
00:24:06,696 --> 00:24:08,155
