01:21:45,359 --> 01:21:48,653
Municipal bonds, Ted.
I'm talking double-A rating.

1269
01:21:48,738 --> 01:21:50,113
The best investment in America.

1270
01:27:22,863 --> 01:27:25,407
Well, I'll give him another 20 minutes.

1271
